  "cards": [
    {
      "id": "sw-01",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "What does swinging mean to you two?\n\nTogether only? Separate rooms? Soft? Full?\n\nDefine it before anything else gets decided.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "Define it"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 3,
      "who_starts": "partnerA",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-02",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "The setting question.\n\nClub, house party, friends, apps?\n\nWhich sounds fun? Which sounds terrifying?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "fun",
        "terrifying"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 4,
      "who_starts": "partnerB",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-03",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "How ready do you feel for the nearest real step?\n\nToday. Honestly.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "Honestly"
      ],
      "type": "unspoken",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-04",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "What needs to be agreed in advance?\n\nWhat are you comfortable deciding in the room?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "in advance",
        "in the room"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "partnerA",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-05",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "For him:\n\nIn a room where everything is visible, where does the measuring-up worry show up for you?\n\nSay it plainly. Every man in that room has a version of it.\n\nThen, for her: tell him what you'd actually be noticing.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "measuring-up"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "mf",
      "sort_order": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-05f",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "Whichever of you worries more about performing:\n\nIn a room where everything is visible, where does that worry show up?\n\nSay it plainly.\n\nThen the other: say what you'd actually be noticing.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "performing"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "flexible",
      "sort_order": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-06",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "For her:\n\nBeing read first and approached most comes with a job: reading the room for safety while trying to have fun in it.\n\nWhat would make that job lighter?\n\nThen, for him: how do you make the room feel safer without hovering?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "reading the room"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "mf",
      "sort_order": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-06f",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "Whichever of you gets read first and approached most:\n\nThat comes with a job: reading the room for safety while trying to have fun in it.\n\nWhat would make the job lighter?\n\nThen the other: how do you help without hovering?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "approached most"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "flexible",
      "sort_order": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-07",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "What if someone approaches you two mid-party...\n\nand only one of you is interested?\n\nPlay it out. Both versions.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "only one of you"
      ],
      "type": "whatIf",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-08",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "Sexual health, said plainly.\n\nProtection. Testing cadence. The non-negotiables.\n\nGet specific enough that nothing is left to assumption.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "non-negotiables"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 6,
      "who_starts": "partnerB",
      "is_sensitive": true,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": "If you disagreed on any non-negotiable, that item gets settled outside a party.\n\nNever at one.",
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-09",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "The exit plan.\n\nWhat happens when one of you wants to leave and the other is having the night of their life?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "exit plan"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "partnerA",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-10",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "Your favorite memory of the two of you being a team in a room full of strangers.\n\nTell it like a story. Take the long version.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "a team"
      ],
      "type": "coolOff",
      "intensity": 3,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sw-11",
      "deck_id": "swinging",
      "text": "The Room Signal.\n\nPick the word or gesture that means \"find me\" in any room.\n\nPractice it once now, seriously.\n\nThen once more, laughing.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "find me"
      ],
      "type": "closingRitual",
      "intensity": 4,
      "who_starts": "both",
